---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Special Events - Ohr HaTorah" pageTitle="Special Events & Community Gatherings" pageIcon="fas fa-star">
    <p class="intro-text"><strong>Special event information and details will be posted as events are planned and scheduled.</strong></p>

    <p class="description">Throughout the year, we host various special events and gatherings including:</p>

    <div class="events-grid">
        <div class="event-card">
            <i class="fas fa-utensils"></i>
            <h3>Community Dinners</h3>
            <p>Fellowship meals and celebrations</p>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
            <i class="fas fa-microphone"></i>
            <h3>Guest Speakers</h3>
            <p>Teaching from visiting rabbis and scholars</p>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
            <i class="fas fa-music"></i>
            <h3>Musical Concerts</h3>
            <p>Messianic Jewish music and worship</p>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
            <i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i>
            <h3>Educational Workshops</h3>
            <p>Hebrew language and Jewish culture</p>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
            <h3>Interfaith Dialogues</h3>
            <p>Building bridges in our community</p>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
            <i class="fas fa-child"></i>
            <h3>Youth Activities</h3>
            <p>Special programs for children and teens</p>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
            <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
            <h3>Volunteer Opportunities</h3>
            <p>Serving our local community</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
        <p>These events provide opportunities for deeper fellowship, learning, and outreach. All are welcome to participate in these meaningful gatherings.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-box">
        <h4><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> For more information about upcoming special events:</h4>
        <div class="contact-links">
            <a href="tel:+17144061513"><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> (714) 406-1513</a>
            <a href="mailto:OhrHaTorahOC@gmail.com"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> OhrHaTorahOC@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
    .intro-text {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .description {
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .events-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .event-card {
        background: var(--gray-100);
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .event-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .event-card i {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: var(--primary-blue);
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .event-card h3 {
        color: var(--primary-blue);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }

    .event-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .info-box {
        background: var(--gold-light);
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .info-box p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .contact-box {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, #004080 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 25px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-box h4 {
        margin: 0 0 15px 0;
        color: white;
    }

    .contact-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 20px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .contact-links a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .contact-links a:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    }
</style>
